{"id":150487,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/德国总统取消对蒂森-克虏伯巴西工厂的访问日程/","date":"2011-05-07T10:00:24Z","modified":"2011-05-07T10:00:24Z","title":"德国总统取消对蒂森-克虏伯巴西工厂的访问日程","content":"<div>\n<p><strong><span> </span></strong> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></p>\n<p><span>里约热内卢</span></p>\n<p><span>德国联邦总统武尔夫取消了在访问巴西期间参观卢蒂森</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&#8211;</span><span>克虏伯钢铁集团位于里约热内卢的工厂的日程。武尔夫称取消参观日程的原因是蒂森克虏伯集团正在进行</span><span>“</span><span>临时结构调整</span><span>”</span><span>，其结果还无法预见。这家德国最大的钢铁集团计划通过所宣布的公司重组计划裁减</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">35000</span><span>个工作岗位。公司目前总共拥有员工</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>万</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>千人。里约热内卢是联邦总统武尔夫为期一周的拉美之行的最后一站。里约热内卢蒂森克虏伯钢铁厂投资额超过五十亿欧元，是该集团历史上最昂贵的一次投资。武尔夫在圣保罗外贸商会发表讲话，要求核电厂达到全球统一标准。他还呼吁致力于</span><span>“</span><span>绿色增长</span><span>“</span><span>，认为德国和巴西可以发挥先锋作用。</span> <span>在访问巴西之前，武尔夫访问了墨西哥和哥斯达黎加。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15057600%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%AF%B9%E8%92%82%E6%A3%AE-%E5%85%8B%E8%99%8F%E4%BC%AF%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%B7%A5%E5%8E%82%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br />